org.apache.spark.sql.api.java

Interface UDFRegistration

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JavaHiveContext, JavaSQLContext

    public interface UDFRegistration
    A collection of functions that allow Java users to register UDFs. In order to handle functions of varying airities with minimal boilerplate for our users, we generate classes and functions for each airity up to 22. The code for this generation can be found in comments in this trait.
